subject: French Open (Tennis)
Tennis
lead_paragraph: Maria Sharapova rallied to beat Garbiñe Muguruza, 1-6, 7-5, 6-1, and Eugenie Bouchard fought off Carla Suárez Navarro, 7-6 (4), 2-6, 7-5, in the quarterfinals on Tuesday.
